---
import '@fontsource-variable/space-grotesk';
import '@fontsource/ibm-plex-sans/400.css';
import '@fontsource/ibm-plex-sans/600.css';
import '../../styles/gaia-standalone.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="GAIA standalone: rooted seasonal reading surface with grey-black root systems and silver signal strings."
    />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#5c5f66" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/martin-portfolio/index.css" />
    <title>GAIA | Root Signal Surface</title>
  </head>
  <body class="gaia-standalone">
    <div class="gaia-shell">
      <header class="gaia-header">
        <a class="gaia-brand" href="/gaia/">
          <span class="gaia-mark">GAIA</span>
          <span class="gaia-tagline">Root Signal Surface</span>
        </a>
        <nav class="gaia-nav" aria-label="GAIA navigation">
          <a href="/astral-year/app/">Open full app</a>
          <a href="/astral-year/glossary/">Glossary</a>
          <a href="/projects/astral/">Project</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <main class="gaia-main">
        <section class="gaia-hero" aria-labelledby="gaia-title">
          <div class="gaia-hero-grid">
            <div>
              <p class="gaia-eyebrow">Gaialogy interface</p>
              <h1 id="gaia-title">Seasonal readings through root pressure and silver threads.</h1>
              <p>
                GAIA keeps interpretation grounded in relation, seasonality, and lived consequence. Signals stay
                visible as connected strands, not isolated fragments.
              </p>
              <div class="gaia-actions">
                <a class="gaia-button primary" href="/astral-year/app/">Open GAIA app</a>
                <a class="gaia-button secondary" href="/astral-year/glossary/">Read sign glossary</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <aside class="gaia-signal-panel" aria-label="Signal frame">
              <h2>System Signals</h2>
              <ul>
                <li><span>Substrate</span><strong>Soil and social ground</strong></li>
                <li><span>Tracing</span><strong>Silver continuity threads</strong></li>
                <li><span>Pressure</span><strong>Seasonal and relational load</strong></li>
                <li><span>Use</span><strong>Practical orientation rhythm</strong></li>
              </ul>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="gaia-section" aria-labelledby="gaia-zones-title">
          <div class="gaia-section-head">
            <p class="gaia-kicker">System zones</p>
            <h2 id="gaia-zones-title">Three visible layers for reading pressure and relation.</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="gaia-grid" aria-label="GAIA surfaces">
            <article class="gaia-card">
              <p class="gaia-node">Node 01</p>
              <h3>Rooted Context</h3>
              <p>Read signs through social and relational ground conditions, not detached celestial abstraction.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="gaia-card">
              <p class="gaia-node">Node 02</p>
              <h3>Silver Strings</h3>
              <p>Track connections between pressure, care, and adaptation as linked interpretive threads.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="gaia-card">
              <p class="gaia-node">Node 03</p>
              <h3>Practical Rhythm</h3>
              <p>Use daily and seasonal cues as governance for attention, timing, and action under uncertainty.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="gaia-threadfield" aria-labelledby="gaia-thread-title">
          <h2 id="gaia-thread-title">Thread map excerpt</h2>
          <div class="gaia-thread-grid">
            <article>
              <h3>Strata A</h3>
              <p>Root stress rises when symbolic conflict and governance deadlines align.</p>
            </article>
            <article>
              <h3>Strata B</h3>
              <p>Silver strings identify where care obligations and policy boundaries intersect.</p>
            </article>
            <article>
              <h3>Strata C</h3>
              <p>Surface signals convert hidden system load into usable timing decisions.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
